commentAnnotations.text: Progression detected by bone scan at an unscheduled visit prior to week 25 will require the same criteria for documentation of disease progression as week 13 with a confirmatory scan at least 6 weeks later or at the next scheduled scan.

commentAnnotations.text: May not have received any growth factors within 7 days or blood transfusions within 28 days prior to the hematology values obtained at screening.
Waivers to the inclusion criteria will NOT be allowed.
Once a subject has been enrolled, the clinical trial protocol applies to the subject.
